OL,6,FStaff at hospitals in Nottingham will
OL,7,Fpatrol the hospital grounds to offer
OL,8,Fadvice to smokers in a bid to help
OL,9,Fmore people quit.
OL,11,FNottingham University Hospitals NHS
OL,12,FTrust's (NUH) two new 'Smokefree
OL,13,Fengagement workers' will patrol
OL,14,FQueen's Medical Centre and City
OL,15,FHospital.
OL,17,FThe trust says that although its
OL,18,Fhospitals have officially been smoke-
OL,19,Ffree since 2006, smoking is still an
OL,20,Fissue and causes regular complaints
OL,21,Ffrom staff and visitors.
