OL,3,CStaff at Nottingham hospitals on
OL,4,Cpatrol to help smokers quit
OL,6,FSmokers will be offered nicotine-
OL,7,Freplacement therapy and can be
OL,8,Freferred to a 12-week stop smoking
OL,9,Fprogramme.
OL,11,FMohammed Khan is one of the new staff
OL,12,Fthat will patrol hospital grounds, and
OL,13,Fsaid: "We are completely non-
OL,14,Fjudgemental."
