OL,3,CStaff at Nottingham hospitals on
OL,4,Cpatrol to help smokers quit
OL,6,FHe said: "We know the hospital can be
OL,7,Fa stressful place, for staff, patients
OL,8,Fand visitors alike - anything can
OL,9,Fhappen in a day - we're not there to
OL,10,Fremove smokers from the site, but just
OL,11,Fto make them aware of what support is
OL,12,Favailable."
OL,14,FThe scheme comes as smokers are
OL,15,Fencouraged to take part 'Stoptober'
OL,16,Fwhich helps people kick the habit for
OL,17,F28 days which is then said to make
OL,18,Fthem five times more likely to quit
OL,19,Ffor good.
