OL,3,CStaff at Nottingham hospitals on
OL,4,Cpatrol to help smokers quit
OL,6,FSince its launch by Public Health
OL,7,FEngland 12 years ago, Stoptober has
OL,8,Fhelped more than 2.5 million people
OL,9,Fgive up smoking.
OL,11,FZahida Niazi, Smokefree Lead at NUH,
OL,12,Fsaid: "We recognise that smoking is an
OL,13,Faddiction and some people find it
OL,14,Fdifficult to stop. But smokers are not
OL,15,Fjust putting their own health at risk,
OL,16,Fbut the health of anyone around them.
