OL,3,CStaff at Nottingham hospitals on
OL,4,Cpatrol to help smokers quit
OL,6,F"Smokers can vape on the grounds as an
OL,7,Falternative to smoking. Vaping is 95%
OL,8,Fless harmful than smoking and passive
OL,9,Fvaping is not the same as passive
OL,10,Fsmoking as vapes do not contain
OL,11,Ftobacco."
OL,13,FGovernment research shows that as soon
OL,14,Fas two weeks after stopping, at least
OL,15,Ftwo in every five smokers feel they
OL,16,Fhave more energy, feel healthier, and
OL,17,Fhave improved breathing.
